        "description": "The CFD solver must operate under a documented quality management system with version-controlled source, automated regression test suite covering >90% of solver modules, and a traceable issue-resolution log. All simulation scripts are archived under configuration management."
      },
      "rationale": "The CFD solver (OpenFOAM v9, custom hemolysis module) is maintained under a Git-based QMS with CI regression tests covering 94% of modules. All simulation scripts, mesh generation macros, and post-processing routines are archived in a versioned repository. Issue log reviewed and closed for all critical items prior to this assessment. Achieved Gradation 4 meets the required Gradation 4 for MRL 5."
