        "type": "AcceptanceCriteria",
        "name": "Test conditions acceptance criteria",
        "description": "Experimental boundary conditions (inlet flow rate, outlet pressure, fluid temperature, rotational speed) must be documented with measurement uncertainty for all 5 operating points. Deviations from nominal must be quantified."
      },
      "rationale": "All 5 operating points (2 L/min/2500 RPM, 3 L/min/2500 RPM, 4 L/min/2500 RPM, 4 L/min/3500 RPM, 5 L/min/3500 RPM) have fully documented boundary conditions with calibrated instrumentation uncertainty (flow: ±0.5%, pressure: ±0.3%, temperature: ±0.2°C). Deviations from nominal are <1% for all parameters. Gradation 3 achieved and required."
    },
    {
