      },
      "rationale": "Validation experiments used the FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry (identical to COU geometry), glycerol-water analogue at 37°C matched viscosity (3.5 cP), and operating points spanning the full COU envelope. Reynolds number and flow coefficient similarity is documented. Geometry, fluid, and operating envelope match between validation and COU is complete. Gradation 4 achieved and required."
